{"tid":1659994,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"孔乙娥一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着她笑","createTime":"2019-10-17T08:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T12:00:51.000Z","uid":74203,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4819b23cd3cf3833d769f19eac9bd555f2cb8c8d","tid":1659994,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:55:13.000Z","msg":"孔乙娥一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着她笑，有的叫道，「孔乙娥，你cv上又添上新傷疤了！」她不回答，對櫃裏說，「溫兩碗酒，要一碟茴香豆。」便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又被人家屌了！」孔乙娥睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你在立會被撚，吊着打。」孔乙娥便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「政治不能算撚&hellip;&hellip;政治！&hellip;&hellip;做戲的事，能算撚麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「共建家園」，什麼「者乎」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：天安門內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月20，出來吃茴香豆！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c63810e5e291edd98902e6aed904c03c623a0ccf","tid":1659994,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b6e06a262902fbde56acfb38ef2c7f860c08ce48","tid":1659994,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:58:14.000Z","msg":"【行動】西九遊行<span style=\"color: red;\">要大量針對強國人文宣</span>！<br />\n務求<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">輸出革命</span></strong>！附詳盡策略：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1659090</a>"},{"pid":"0d757e649c4a1a59c87b87b70f0e2a511e365a06","tid":1659994,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923ea75d9232e05bc450cd4c322c2497f62a5ec5","tid":1659994,"uid":241449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T12:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces